    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Clothing for the upper body, usually as womenswear. The front is made of two parts whose crossing forms a V-shape decolletage. The two parts can be attached at the waist in several ways; usually straps or buttons.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
